raw:
aut-num:        AS212024
as-name:        RISSON
org:            ORG-RSN5-RIPE
sponsoring-org: ORG-PMTA6-RIPE
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        |
remarks:        | RISSON AUTONOMOUS SYSTEM
remarks:        | Visit https://as212024.net for further information
remarks:        |
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        | Abuse Handling
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        We kindly ask you to send all abuse reports to abuse@risson.space.
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        | Points of Presence
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        See https://as212024.peeringdb.net for an up-to-date list.
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        | Notes about preferences
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        Transits localprefed at 100
remarks:        IXP RS routes localprefed at 150
remarks:        IXP direct peers localprefed at 200
remarks:        PNI direct peers localprefed at 250
remarks:        Localpref is applied per-neighbor, not per-circuit
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        | Import policy applied from ALL peers
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        * Netmasks filtered IPv4 ge /8 le /24 IPv6 ge /12 le /48
remarks:        * Drop RPKI invalid
remarks:        * Max-route limit set for non-transits
remarks:        * Drop RFC1918 etc.
remarks:        * Drop paths with bogon ASNs
remarks:        * Drop paths with transit ASNs
remarks:        * Drop ASPA invalid paths
remarks:        
remarks:        +=====================================================================
remarks:        | Transits
remarks:        +=====================================================================

export:         to AS58057 announce AS212024:AS-RISSON

remarks:

remarks:

remarks:
